  When two observers intersect polytopes (P_A âˆ© P_B),
  they find SHARED HEDGING STRATEGIES.
  
  Intersection dimension measures:
  "How many ways can we BOTH hedge while agreeing?"

GEMINI'S GAUGE FREEDOM â€” CONFIRMED:
  The 9D is not "9 ways to pick a deterministic story."
  It's "9 ways to WEIGHT a portfolio of stories."
  
  Agency lives in HOW you hedge, not WHICH story is true.
  
  This is the Rashomon Effect at the probabilistic level:
  Even at extreme points, you must tell multiple stories.
```

